title: SNP conference: Aberdeen venue and meeting delegates
text:
Media playback is unsupported on your device SNP conference: Aberdeen venue and meeting delegates 16 October 2015 Last updated at 14:56 BST
The largest ever conference for the SNP has followed the party's record-breaking election win in the general election in May
Adam Fleming meets some of those at the Aberdeen venue, and hears about the party's own magazine, events for delegates and what is on sale in its shop.
Read more Daily Politics and Sunday Politics highlights of 2015
